{%- comment -%}
  salon-menu-schema.liquid  —  GEO structured data for the partner-salon service-menu pages.

  Emits a HairSalon + OfferCatalog (priced services) + BreadcrumbList so AI engines (Google AI
  Overviews, Copilot) and Google rich results can cite "<salon> price" — the high-intent query
  these pages rank for (Azta #1.1, David's #7) but previously had ZERO schema for.

  Gated by page.handle (partner-salon menu pages only). Prices are PHP, confirmed current by the
  operator 2026-06 (source: the on-page service-menu). Each ranged service uses AggregateOffer
  (lowPrice = "from"); fixed-price services use Offer.

  bd hairmnl-theme-0kv3.1 (GEO Capitalize epic 0kv3).
  {# MIGRATION-DEBT: bespoke P6 GEO schema. Port to OS-2.0 as a metaobject-driven section.
     reason = Smart SEO does NOT emit Service/OfferCatalog for these custom pages; the existing
     hairsalon-schema.liquid (own studios) is the precedent pattern. See os2-migration/customization-audit.md. #}
{%- endcomment -%}

